data.description: Welcome to 6 Gaylord St, this young 2015 built colonial is the gem you've been waiting for. Boasting water views of Indian Lake and set in an established dead end neighborhood the location along will have you sold. The main level flaunts a seamless open concept floor plan leading to the cabinet packed granite and stainless steel kitchen, complete with center island and slider out to the deck. The second level hosts the three bedrooms, a front to back primary suite with walk in closet and full bath, the two additional bedrooms share the home's second full bathroom: both generously sized with tons of natural light and closet storage. The partially finished, walk out lower level offers endless potential, insulated and roughed, this canvas could be a media room, home gym, potential in-law or au-pair suite. Easy access to major routes, Assumption College, and all that Indian Lake has to offer.
